title: Watch: SM’s J-Min Makes Comeback With “Alive” Music Video
text: Pin   March 20, SM artist J-Min released the music video for her digital single “Alive,” her first since August last year, when she released “ Ready For Your Love ,” featuring NCT’s Johnny.   The singer also appeared on the March 19 broadcast of MBC’s “ King of Masked Singer .” You can watch her performance here: J-Min, in addition to promotions as a singer, has been working as a musical actress. Currently, she is starring in “Boys Over Flowers The Musical.” J-Min will be taking the stage at “M!Countdown” on March 23 to perform her new song live.
